 AGENT RESPONSE 
Nice catch — you were 100% right. I fixed it. 🐶✅

What I changed
──────────────

1) Freeze is now 10 seconds
• Shot effect changed from short slow to full freeze:
  ◦ freezeDurationMs: 10000

2) Freeze now affects only the attacker
• Added explicit attacker freeze state:
  ◦ attackerFrozenUntil
• In attacker AI:
  ◦ if frozen → attacker velocity set to 0
  ◦ player + whole game continue normally
• So no global freeze anymore.

3) Added timer at top of screen
• New top HUD label in gameplay area:
  ◦ Old Man Freeze: READY
  ◦ on hit: Old Man Freeze: 9.9s ... 0.0s
• Updates every frame.

4) Hardened projectile collision callback
• Made overlap callback robust so it always treats the projectile as the projectile and won’t accidentally affect the wrong object.

5) Text cleanup
• Updated wording from slow-shot to freeze-shot in:
  ◦ Title controls line
  ◦ Left-panel legend

───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

If you want next, I can add a cooldown timer too (separate from freeze timer), so player can see when the next shot is available.

